      </fig>
      <p>The dashboard also contains information about the input parameters (<xref ref-type="fig" rid="fig-8">Fig. 8</xref>). Advanced users can browse details about the tools’ execution: executable files, command-line arguments and logs (<xref ref-type="fig" rid="fig-9">Fig. 9</xref>).</p>
